Class ISO8601DateTimeInterval

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.geodesy.ISO8601DateTimePoint
org.opensextant.geodesy.ISO8601DateTimeInterval
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<ISO8601DateTimePoint>
public class ISO8601DateTimeInterval extends ISO8601DateTimePoint
The ISO8601DateTimeInterval class is a simple wrapper for a time interval with a start and end time.
